name: Summoning ETH Celestial Skies
description:
Digital Painting / Motion - In
collaboration with my friend
@Creyety. After traveling for weeks in
search of the elusive ETH crystals,
the monk came upon the land where
the earth meets the sky. Dejected and
losing hope of ever finding the
crystals, a beam of light burst forth
from the ground. The stars hummed
against the light, and a great structure
emerged. There, the crystals which
had laid dormant, hidden in time, was
summoned by the monk's very
presence.
